com.misc.common.moplaf.solver

Interface Solution

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SolutionLp
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SolutionImpl, SolutionLpImpl

    public interface Solution
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Solution'.

    A Solution is some solution to a problem formulation Generator and is produced by some SolutionProvider, typically a Solver.

    A Solution contains

    • information relative to the solution for some variable: element SolutionVar
    • information relative to the solution for some constraint: element SolutionCons

    The following features are supported:

    • Provider
    • Solution Nr
    • Code
    • Solver As Initial Solution
    • Elements
    • Vars
    • Cons
    • Goals
    See Also:
